<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.7">
<l>taṇiyum poḻutillai nīraṇaṅ kāṭuti raṉṉaimīr</l>
<l>piṇiyu moḻikiṉṟa tillai peruku mituvallāl</l>
<l>maṇiyi ṉaṇiniṟa māyaṉ ṟamaraṭi nīṟukoṇ</l>
<l>ṭaṇiya muyaliṉ maṟṟillai kaṇṭī riv vaṇaṅkukkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is not the time to calm [her], you will dance as demonesses, mothers,</l>
<l>and the illness will not pass, it will increase, except for this:</l>
<l>There is nothing other than the effort to adorn [her] with ashes from the feet of his people,</l>
<l>the Dark one with decorative sapphire-like colour, see, for the girl.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
